seo: 帆软报表,任意文件读取漏洞,CNVD-2018-04757,漏洞检测,指纹识别
summary: 该插件用于检测帆软报表 V8 系统是否存在任意文件读取漏洞（CNVD-2018-04757），并进行指纹识别和漏洞验证。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the FineReport V8 system has arbitrary file reading vulnerability (CNVD-2018-04757), and perform fingerprint identification and vulnerability verification.
